name: BB95 Realistic Mix
description:
This model is a mix of various models. This is the mix I use on other model I made

It's doing well on generating photorealistic male and female, SFW and NSFW.

I HIGHLY recommend to use Hires Fix to have better results

Below is an example prompt.

Positive:

Use the prompt from posted images

Negative:

I recommend to use bad-hands-v5, easynegatives, bad-artist

Settings :

Steps: 30-150

Sampler: DDIM or UniPC

CFG scale: 7-14

Size: from 512x512 to 750x750

Denoising strength: 0.6

Clip skip: 1

Hires upscale: 2

Hires steps: 30-150

Hires upscaler: Latent (nearest)
